privacy.title: Application Privacy
privacy.paragraph: Cuscon doesn't send or collect any data.
paragraph.description: We create transparent icons that are visible on any background. To accomplish this we outline every image with a black outline.
paragraph.info: If you want to create your own Icon-Pack you can read this article.
icons.smart-things.info: The icon-pack's logo is inspired from this one.
icons.add.info:
If you want to add more icons feel free to open an issue or a pull request on the Github Repository.
You can also send a icon-request (from the app) to miep_hd@froxot.com.
